description:
SUMMER VENGEANCE continues as yet another wrestler is eliminated from the tournament. Who gets beaten and fucked on the mat this time?

Both wrestlers are in the lightweight class, however the Badger has much more mat experience. Only one can move forward to the next round of competition. In this match you’ll see leg scissors, complete submissions, and some brutal arm holds. Plus some hot hardcore fingering and domination on the mat. In the end, one girl loses and the winner fucks the shit out of her in rd4, leaving her defeated and exhausted in a pool of her own sweat on the mat.
title: SUMMER VENGEANCE The Kitten(0-1) Ranked 13th The Badger(2-4) Ranked 14th
